%!PS-Adobe-3.0
%%Title: CADlink Filter Definitions
%%Creator: Manhattan RIP X
%%EndComments

% Image filter procedures
/ASCIIHexDecode where { pop } { /ASCIIHexDecode /filter load def } ifelse
/ASCII85Decode  where { pop } { /ASCII85Decode  /filter load def } ifelse
/LZWDecode      where { pop } { /LZWDecode      /filter load def } ifelse
/FlateDecode    where { pop } { /FlateDecode    /filter load def } ifelse
/RunLengthDecode where { pop } { /RunLengthDecode /filter load def } ifelse

%%EOF
